### 注册普通用户
POST http://localhost:9001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "password": "Demo@123456",
  "nickname": "演示用户",
  "phone": "13800000000",
  "email": "demo@tdep.local"
}

### 管理员登录
POST http://localhost:9001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123456"
}

### 普通用户登录
POST http://localhost:9001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "password": "Demo@123456"
}

### 获取当前用户信息，将登录返回的 accessToken 粘贴到 Bearer 后面
GET http://localhost:9001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 退出登录，将登录返回的 accessToken 粘贴到 Bearer 后面
POST http://localhost:9001/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
